    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin((0.39 / v2))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.59) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.17)) - wp.abs((tmp + 0.81 * v2 + 0.12)))
    v2 = v0
    v0 = (v0 / 0.22)
    tmp = (wp.cos(0.65) * wp.sin((v2 + 0.90 - v0 + 0.21)))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.sin((v1 + 0.94 * v1 + 0.51)))
    tmp = 0.89
    data[tid] = v0
